<Author>Benfromsydney
<Content>Ruined one full day of our short break We are a married couple who travel quite regularly and book through hotel websites everytime. We booked this one on the day we arrived and when we got to the hotel the staff were quite rude. Not thinking anything of it, we proceeded to our room and found they had put us in a twin room. so we went back to reception as we had booked a double room. On explaining that there was an error the 2 men on reception were abusive, rude and trying to tell us that in europe a double room means 2 singles. we asked for a refund and they would not give it to us. we stayed calm and polite through this and just wanted to leave then after much more yelling and insults from the men in both english and spanish we were given another room (110) which was a dark, pokey room in the back of the hotel with a mossy brick wall as the view (the first room they gave us had a balcony) This hotel is cheap and accordingly nasty, the staff are intimidating and rude. As we left they joked in spanish they would use my Credit Card details to buy his wife a gift. (thinking we could not understand) This was a simple mistake they could have rectified in seconds and instead they upset us and ruined our holiday. Dont stay here! other hotels in barcelona for the same price are 10 times better. PS yes, i did cancel my CC. 
